    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/87e4a243faf60a3a94b44c4a04ad5928.poster.avif?t=1741346729\" width=620 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/87e4a243faf60a3a94b44c4a04ad5928.webm?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/87e4a243faf60a3a94b44c4a04ad5928.mp4?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>这是关于爱丽丝梦游仙境之后的故事。<br>遗忘是最恶毒的魔咒。成年后的爱丽丝也经历了不那么童话般的生活，也不再做梦，也意味着有关仙境的一切正在慢慢消失。仙境里的人们甚至忘记了自己为何存在，在一切消散之前，柴郡猫施展了幻影魔法，想要找到爱丽丝，希望她能再拯救一次仙境。<br>但柴郡猫也记不清咒语了，错误的法术让它穿越到了平行世界，这个世界里的爱丽丝根本就不知道仙境的存在。<br>为了使仙境不被遗忘，柴郡猫带着各个平行世界的爱丽丝回到仙境，试图唤醒人们的记忆，尽管经历了一次又一次的失败，柴郡猫依旧相信着，他会找到对的那个爱丽丝。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/ba19bb1e101ab3cda41a19be349147b1.webp?t=1741346729\" width=410 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/ccc385d4a6344a116e05f2c60a7f9fac.poster.avif?t=1741346729\" width=640 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/ccc385d4a6344a116e05f2c60a7f9fac.webm?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/ccc385d4a6344a116e05f2c60a7f9fac.mp4?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>扮演截然不同的爱丽丝,利用不同的能力不同的卡组来战胜敌人,每个爱丽丝都有属于自己的故事!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/f0b0827363f452d507553b3fc0c371bd.webp?t=1741346729\" width=410 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/13cfad48e0d59d04b8de434767568623.poster.avif?t=1741346729\" width=640 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/13cfad48e0d59d04b8de434767568623.webm?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/13cfad48e0d59d04b8de434767568623.mp4?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>被施了魔咒的&quot;怪物们&quot;本不是真正的怪物,打败怪物后即可解除魔咒,发现他们的另一面!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/e962908a2a74504e8f4f48745a09a8ee.webp?t=1741346729\" width=410 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/f32cf047c769f24af003f3b57a660526.poster.avif?t=1741346729\" width=640 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/f32cf047c769f24af003f3b57a660526.webm?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/f32cf047c769f24af003f3b57a660526.mp4?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>看似随处可见的扑克牌,此刻将成为你最大的战斗力!扑克兵可以获得不同的符文来增加战斗力!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/3e6d026b7202bb5bfc24cd2fc1b748cd.webp?t=1741346729\" width=410 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/47794259177e9fb31d65334c50d487e5.poster.avif?t=1741346729\" width=620 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/47794259177e9fb31d65334c50d487e5.webm?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166980/extras/47794259177e9fb31d65334c50d487e5.mp4?t=1741346729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>将相同点数或者花色的扑克兵排列在一起,即可获得加强效果,他们没有情感但很善于战斗!</strong>",
